title: Local arts projects to receive over £5m in next round of Creative People and Places ...
text: ( Source : Arts Council England ) Arts Council England today ( 21 October ) announced £5,208,951 in funding for six successful local arts projects in the latest round of its Creative People and Places funding programme. Funded by the Arts
